#Task Scheduler (VERY GOOD ONE)
📜 Problem Statement

You are given tasks represented by characters:

["A","A","A","B","B","B"]

Each task takes 1 unit time.
There is a cooldown n between same tasks.

👉 Return minimum time required to finish all tasks.

💡 Example
Input: tasks = ["A","A","A","B","B","B"], n = 2  
Output: 8  
Explanation: A B idle A B idle A B
